      <title>印度央行维持关键利率，坚持鹰派立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/india-central-bank-holds-key-rate-sticks-with-hawkish-stance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行周四连续第六次会议维持基准利率不变，并保持鹰派政策立场，表明利率将在更长时间内保持较高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/india-central-bank-holds-key-rate-sticks-with-hawkish-stance</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 04:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Elara Capital：印度央行在 2025 财年第二季度之前不会降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-08/elara-capital-no-rbi-rate-cuts-before-2q-fy25-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Elara Capital 高级副总裁兼经济学家 Garima Kapoor 表示，她认为印度在 2025 财年第二季度之前不会降息。她与哈斯琳达·阿明就“彭博市场：亚洲”进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-08/elara-capital-no-rbi-rate-cuts-before-2q-fy25-video</guid>
