    <item>
      <title>美元创历史新高，新加坡人涌向马来西亚讨价还价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/myr-usd-strong-singapore-dollar-sgd-vs-malaysia-ringgit-a-new-year-bonus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[李若彤 (Carman Lee) 从新加坡乘坐七个半小时的巴士回到马来西亚西北部的家乡怡保，迎接即将到来的农历新年。新加坡威斯汀酒店的员工还有另一个理由庆祝这个节日：当地美元创历史新高，使得所有东西相对林吉特都便宜得多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/myr-usd-strong-singapore-dollar-sgd-vs-malaysia-ringgit-a-new-year-bonus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 04:15:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
