    <item>
      <title>中国消费者价格下降速度为2009年以来最快</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/china-s-consumer-prices-drop-at-fastest-pace-since-2009</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，中国的消费者价格出现了自全球金融危机以来最快的跌幅，这给政府带来了支持经济反弹的压力，而经济反弹却扰乱了市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/china-s-consumer-prices-drop-at-fastest-pace-since-2009</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 01:40:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监管层出人意料的人事变动后中国股市涨势延续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/china-stocks-rise-after-naming-of-new-top-markets-regulator</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，中国股市继续上涨，此前当局出人意料地更换了中国证券监管机构负责人，表明了遏制 7 万亿美元暴跌的更坚定决心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/china-stocks-rise-after-naming-of-new-top-markets-regulator</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 01:35:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
